Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六有爽子做飯 輕鬆真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 之前的初次放學後拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果沒有吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我居然忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全進入了吃拉麵狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然吉田同學看上去是遺憾的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不承認拉麵是種簡單的食物 $%#@*
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之後一起去喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了吉田拉麵談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同學 吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃咖喱嗎 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是吃咖喱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裡是黑沼家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:19:31.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻譯:キョン 老虎　校譯:キョン　時間:キョン　後期:風一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天無視我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友打來的電話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子 今天晚上的晚餐是拉麵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫「拉麵哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去「拉麵復仇」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去吃拉麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還沒有把咖喱裝盤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點點事媽媽來做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次把朋友帶回家哦 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子要和朋友一起吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近說過很開心這樣的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 最近也比以前晚回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:51.69,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD8F0E8&\4c&H616484&\pos(420,389)}第六話 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是男的還是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:56.85,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2F4F9&\3c&H70B9A9&\pos(424,129)}第七話\N星期六的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是可喜可賀的初次拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們還不知道你手機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 如果買了的話就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 千鶴 今天帶朋友來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 算便宜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是敵不過千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都想讓你嘗嘗這裡吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推薦是味噌拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就味噌拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要醬油拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了推薦是味噌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒水了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁顧客還沒發覺的時候換好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才好像是真田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,436)}現在比較忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是龍呀 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是龍的家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 味噌拉麵久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大叔的拉麵最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家一起吃變的更好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 慢慢坐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是你家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的關係很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同學和真田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 放輕鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和朋友在一起玩去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵餓 還有味噌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳一的耳朵...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會發消息給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的男朋友是大學的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫「現在的」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子到時候也會知道成人世界的精彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成人世界的精彩的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人大人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你曾打倒過99個男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 99連勝那個奇怪的記錄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不奇怪 很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都99了 為啥不100連勝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第100人怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你阻止她100連勝 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在最糟糕的時機進來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 難 難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人是戀人關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍你是肯定還是否定 好歹表示下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別肯定 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千鶴是兄弟的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 誰是哥哥誰是弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)}我是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽點是那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你的生日比我的晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有兄弟姐妹 真是令人羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也吐槽那裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱鬧的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他們在一起也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不如把風早也叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別盡讓龍一個人體驗後宮 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後宮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍也覺得只有一個男生很為難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍 手機拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子打給他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我 我可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 打給他看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到龍的號碼 聽到的卻是女生的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早會嚇一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下那個鍵就能通話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 別那麼緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早一定會自己接電話的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得越來越緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這裡很熱鬧 速度過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍一個人太可憐了 叫他快來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(翔太)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 翔太 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是龍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要和龍說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風早同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑 誒 但 龍的手機 誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在真田同學的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了跳 嚇了跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉田同學和矢野同學一起吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後現在和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起很非常非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到風早同學也一起來的話 就變得更加開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我飆自行車 馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然是這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三人中學也一個班級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有二年級和三年級
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍和風早...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知他一直都是這個樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高還在長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學時代的風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是大家的風早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點幼誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為棒球部的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是頭髮從板寸頭剛長長一點的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是龍不管是不是棒球部 卻一直板寸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太棒球很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中沒有加入棒球部 讓小痞很失望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我所不知道的風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的初中時代又會是什麼樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有努力的學習 練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就是運動會了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早應該會參加軟式棒球比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠看到今後的風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠和大家一起留下值得回憶的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起做很多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動會 還有修學旅行 有好多值得期待的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太讓人期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃到很多好吃的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候大家可以一起說「真的好開心啊」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識胡桃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前她曾經幫我撿過卷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼擺出那樣的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是會很受男生歡迎的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受歡迎 受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個類型的怎麼樣 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你還有喜歡的類型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般喜歡?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡真田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最...最喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛差點嚇死我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 貞子 風早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最...喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個「最喜歡」和對我們倆的那個是一樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己到底明不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 應該是沒明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 這也沒什麼不好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往成人的階梯是需要她自己一步一步攀登的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這話從你的嘴裡出來就感覺那麼猥瑣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹 大碗味噌拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 小痞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險 好險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就變得糾纏不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 和其他棒球部的成員比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早的頭髮是不是比較長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙頭髮長的很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是個色狼 而且還是悶騷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我是色狼 也絕不是悶騷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你那一上來就是色狼的開場白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通啦 普通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真是不乾脆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如直接承認自己是大色狼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早 貞子在笑你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 不要笑啊 黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 絕對不是在取笑你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得心跳比平時快好多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為距離比教室裡的座位更近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子 不 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡來 坐到小千的身邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好柔軟啊 真是女孩子的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 王子殿下鬱悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了超有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小P孩的時間已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾蛋 棒球部瘟神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是 趕快回家洗洗睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼荒井老師會...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為太吵被人舉報了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那麼回事 黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這小子的爸爸指教的少年棒球隊出身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還是小P孩的時候就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是龍家裡的常客 臉皮超厚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和這傢伙對視之後 就看到小個子的大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我家裡也有小個子的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(160cm)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞 有沒有遇到過鬼壓床啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候經常有 現在有時也會遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼壓床的時候有沒有在房間裡聽到奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我家房子比較古老了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺的時候經常吱吱嘎嘎的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是因為你有靈感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 昨晚總覺得....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上好重 沒怎麼睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡澡的時候在水裡加點鹽 或許會比較好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅除污穢的鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓身體暖和起來 睡個好覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是除靈的專家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫上老師的忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 小痞 趕快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥 你才應該回家去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(426,436)}已經9點了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倆是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(426,436)}別只在這種時候擺出一副老師的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(426,436)}少囉嗦 解散 解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也會露出這樣的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚真是開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後還會有很多機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會有更多更多開心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友一起度過的星期六的晚上...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不敢相信自己竟然也會有這樣的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我順便去趟便利店 和你同方向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會心跳加速 但這種感覺卻非常愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了哦 紳士同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油哦 紳士同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙真是討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在笑 真是開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會有更多更多開心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你也走這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 離我遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 一個人走夜路多可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我也回家洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你喜歡的類型什麼類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類型?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說胡桃不是你喜歡的類型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲鈍又單純的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當獨特的興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲鈍又單純 就像貞子那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你也不同特地過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來報告的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我「已經和好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在加速的心跳仍然在持續著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能進入這所高中真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家在同一所高中真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大家」也包括我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有風早同學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生就完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微鬧了一下彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧彆扭...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是讓自己安心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前從未見過的他初中時的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有今天第一次見到的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天算是知道了一點點風早同學的另一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學 去便利店買什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買點什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後還會見到更多從未見到的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:25.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:25.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飛滿了紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:36.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いかない　それが答えてなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:36.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 那就是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャボン玉　飛ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂泡泡 飄飄浮浮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:47.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空まではきっと届かない　うちに壊れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:47.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未到達天空就破滅消散而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:53.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いま誰知りたいの永遠じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:53.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我們想要的永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:22:01.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このままずっと　いていたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:22:01.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管想要永遠留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:12.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:12.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飛滿了紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:21.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:21.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只找尋到了屬於我的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:34.88,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(617,356)}第八話 自主訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽映照下的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與以往稍許不同的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 自主訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想告訴你的OP「きみにとどけ」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,タニザワトモフミ(歌手名)以其獨特的聲音和旋律的存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕柔的體現出了好想告訴你的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是Chara演唱ED「片思い」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想告訴你青澀的故事和Chara的聲音真的很配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張CD除了通常版之外還有兩個版本的初回限定版
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有非常吸引人的特典
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要錯過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們下周再見 告訴你
